title: Johnny Winter - 38-32-29 Blues (2001) [FLAC]
description:
A collection of Johnny's early recordings, when he was searchings his own style - before he started his awsome career with Columbia records. Most of the songs were previously released on other compilations. Unfortunately this edit contains no liner notes. As I remember from other releases, Edgar Winter plays Saxophone and keyboards on various tracks.
